    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1937-04-28T14:00:00-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1937-04-28T14:00:00-05:00" n="936"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d936">
                <note rend="inline" type="source">561.35E1/341: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The Chairman of the American Delegation</hi> (<persName
                        type="from">
                        <hi rend="italic">Davis</hi>
                    </persName>) <hi rend="italic">to the <gloss type="to">Secretary of
                            State</gloss>
                    </hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">London</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1937-04-28T20:00:00+01:00"
                            >April 28, 1937—8 p.m.</date>
                        <lb/>[Received April 28—3 p.m.]</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>23. A plenary session today adopted quotas outlined in my No. 21, April 26, 5
                    p.m., and accepted accompanying report of Negotiating Committee<note n="21"
                        xml:id="d936fn21">
                        <hi rend="italic">Proceedings and Documents of the Conference</hi>, p.
                        60.</note> subject, however, to right to pass upon final statement in draft
                    agreement of matters it covers.</p>
                <p>Conference is not releasing quota figures or specific information regarding any
                    of them.</p>
                <p>We have changed text submitted to you in my No. 22, April 27, 8 p.m.,<note n="22"
                        xml:id="d936fn22">Not printed.</note> and will transmit revised text after
                    further discussion with Drafting Committee.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Davis</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
